唔識普通話，我一定會話唔係好識，然後介紹返廣東話比佢知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf7b2bbb2337eb53354328cf9ce8f68e4df0d0b","tid":2488392,"uid":288027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:05:27.000Z","msg":"識聽都係聽台灣節目學返黎<br />\n左講就真係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526fc5e276ba67dba7303323dd661345100b99d0","tid":2488392,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71b854966e0cb23411c004b6c8751ec99b5f7aa9","tid":2488392,"uid":379666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:04:35.000Z","msg":"好明顯唔係恥笑緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n類似覺得香港人d口音好可愛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"係 樓主中文閱讀U<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdb4243d31b9345fceecdf6170b9e3ff6ebbfc6e","tid":2488392,"uid":202095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3664ed149eb5d67702a234a65a92b181abb1ba4b","tid":2488392,"uid":11365,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1323777592b9f01f8c53702753e564d0719b74da","tid":2488392,"uid":223912,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:16:55.000Z","msg":"要靠笑人講嘢唔標準嚟提高自信 優越感<br />\n你話依個民族啲人幾可悲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:22:02.000Z","msg":"古天樂 - 省姐撚撚呔撚<br />\n崔世安 - 笨撚 吹屎眼<br />\n<br />\n香港人笑左呢兩個幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i